events.text:
Okay

What the fuck.

All fucking game.

ALL FUCKING GAME.

I've been here, holding your little bald baby hand.

Spoonfeeding you lore like a mother trying to keep her imbecilic child from starving to death by its own idiocy.

I helped you LEVEL UP, you UNGRATEFUL FUCKFACE, and this is how you repay me? By undoing my life's work?

No. You know what? 

It's my fault. Really. For helping a psychopathic, homicidal, bald lunatic with a pair of scissors stab a bunch of hairdressers and hobos to death. I brought this on myself.

Unbelievable.

Un-fucking-believable.

I hope you're happy, asshole.

...

This isn't over.

This is NOT over.
